enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve traversing and collecting elements based on their relationships in the DOM.
The select method can be used to filter elements that are ancestors of the current elements, similar to the parents method.
The parents method itself returns a collection of parent elements, which can be used to construct assertions about the structure of the DOM.
The select method can be used to verify that the correct elements are being returned by the parents method by comparing the results of both methods.
